{
  "texts": [
    "The lines in the figure are DBM simulation results, and the symbols are the experimental results extracted from Ref.",
    "It can be seen that DBM can accurately describe the bubble deformation process in the SBI process.",
    "The compressible Orszag-Tang (OT) magnetic turbulence problem was first proposed by Orsazg and Tang.",
    "It is widely used to validate the effectiveness of magnetohydrodynamics models due to the complex wave structures that emerge during the evolution of the flow field.",
    "Figure 29 shows the pressure distribution at the line when the OT magnetic turbulence problem develops to steady state [43]."
  ]
}